*California passes first sweeping US law to <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2022/jun/30/california-single-use-plastic-reduce-law-gavin-newsom">reduce single-use plastic</a>.*
<p>
Queensland, Australia, will <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2022/jul/01/queensland-plastics-ban-balloon-releases-and-disposable-coffee-cups-targeted">ban some kinds of single-use plastics</a>.
<p>
Helium is scarce and it is needed for some important uses.
We should not permit it to be used for inflating balloons!

 